channel.title: Changes to client.java never show up!
channel.description: Im running TestScape on my computer and testing it with my laptop. But! The changes I make to client.java never appear! I could delete the file entirely and it would make no difference. I run runserver.bat and log on to my server using my laptop. None of my changes ever appear!!!! I cant ever hope to run a server if its just unedited TestScape! Help?
